run make to build "vw" opengl progarm
program draws a grid 50x50 , each mouse left click
marks a point .
it functions as editor for algorithm input file
and viewer for output file 
right click offers a menu of operations .
write operation will produce targets.txt for 
use as input to main program ( you must add 
number of stalkers ) 
most read operations require existence of 
target.txt and solution.txt

note: before choosing "read solution" you must
choose "read targets"
